  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The real-world observational study was designed to explore lymph metastases and prognoses of
      the Chinese patients with thoracic T1-T3 esophageal cancer
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This trial is a real-world non-interventional observational study. The Chinese patients with
      thoracic T1-T3 esophageal cancer enrolled from Jan.1999 to Jun.2017 were included and the
      study data on pathologically diagnosed patient demographic/tumor biological characteristics
      were collected to evaluate the relevance of lymph metastases and prognoses of the subjects.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
