    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients &gt;= 18 years old;

          -  Patients who received radical resection of esophageal cancer;

          -  Pathologically diagnosed patients with thoracic T1-T3 esophageal cancer after
